|===
| 1S | 2D  |
| 2H | ?   |
|    | 3S  | strong slam-interest, 3*{S}
|    | 4S  | picture jump
|===

NOTE: Picture jumps have priority over kickback and minorwood to
ensure that responder's initial plan doesn't get scuttled.

